OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F399A1779127867
OL,3,CBeatles, boats, and JLR: Mural
OL,4,Ccelebrating town's history nears
OL,5,Ccompletion
OL,7,FA new mural celebrating Halewood's
OL,8,Fhistory has been painted on the town's
OL,9,Fcommunity centre.
OL,11,FThe artwork painted by award-winning
OL,12,Fcartoon illustrator Stuart Harrison
OL,13,Fwas commissioned by Knowlsey Council
OL,14,Fto celebrate Halewood visually.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/12
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,400,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39902
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F399A1779127867
OL,3,CBeatles, boats, and JLR: Mural
OL,4,Ccelebrating town's history nears
OL,5,Ccompletion
OL,7,FThe mural painted on the centre of
OL,8,FCamberley Drive includes references to
OL,9,FTriangle Park, Katarina Johnson-
OL,10,FThompson, St Nicholas' Church, Jaguar
OL,11,FLand Rover, Halewood Water Tower,
OL,12,Fsteam trains, and George Harrison from
OL,13,FThe Beatles, which he hopes means the
OL,14,Fmural will be added to Beatles
OL,15,Fsightseeing itineraries.
OL,17,FStuart said that he thinks having
OL,18,Fartwork across public spaces "doesn't
OL,19,Fhalf revitalise a place".
OL,26,@zD@^OU{D@XO]
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/12
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,400,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39903
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F399A1779127867
OL,3,CBeatles, boats, and JLR: Mural
OL,4,Ccelebrating town's history nears
OL,5,Ccompletion
OL,7,FThe images included in the mural were
OL,8,Fdecided by public consultation.
OL,10,FHe said that the public reaction to
OL,11,Fthe mural has been "99% dead positive.
OL,12,FSome people do go: 'What's all this
OL,13,Fstuff?' so I'm a bit of a history
OL,14,Fguide.
OL,16,F"I'm now very knowledgeable about
OL,17,FKnowsley.
OL,19,F"People say it's a brilliant idea and
OL,20,Fbrightens up the area, something to
OL,21,Fdraw the eye," he said.
OL,26,@sD@TOUxD@AOU{D@AOU}D@NO]
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/12
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,400,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39904
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F399A1779127867
OL,3,CBeatles, boats, and JLR: Mural
OL,4,Ccelebrating town's history nears
OL,5,Ccompletion
OL,7,FThe mural also references the Eagle
OL,8,Fand Child pub, with Stuart saying that
OL,9,Fpeople passing the mural have spoken
OL,10,Fabout remembering their family
OL,11,Fdrinking there in years gone by.
OL,13,FOne of the central images shows
OL,14,FBlackie the War Horse, who belonged to
OL,15,F20-year-old Lieutenant Leonard Comer
OL,16,FWall, a war poet from West Kirby, and
OL,17,Fwho was posted to the Western Front in
OL,18,FSeptember 1915.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/12
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,400,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39905
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F399A1779127867
OL,3,CBeatles, boats, and JLR: Mural
OL,4,Ccelebrating town's history nears
OL,5,Ccompletion
OL,7,FLieutenant Wall was killed at the
OL,8,FBattle of Ypres, but the horse
OL,9,Fcontinued serving until the end of the
OL,10,Fwar despite severe injuries, and later
OL,11,Flived at a horse sanctuary in
OL,12,FHalewood, the town where he is buried.
OL,14,F"I like the horse," Stuart said, "it's
OL,15,Fso dynamic. But loads of people have
OL,16,Fbeen talking about the Titanic," which
OL,17,Fis also pictured in the mural.
OL,26,@vD@AOUvD@SO]vD@bOUxD@`O]
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G5/12
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,400,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39906
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F399A1779127867
OL,3,CBeatles, boats, and JLR: Mural
OL,4,Ccelebrating town's history nears
OL,5,Ccompletion
OL,7,F"Some of them have asked: 'Why have
OL,8,Fyou done that?'" he said, adding that
OL,9,Fthe ship has found a place in the
OL,10,Fdesign because "the owner of White
OL,11,FStar Line lived here" at one time, and
OL,12,Fis buried in St Nicholas church
OL,13,Fgraveyard.
OL,15,F"People go: 'I've lived here all my
OL,16,Flife and never knew that,' so it feels
OL,17,Flike a bit of history."
OL,26,@oD@AOUpD@PO]rD@POUsD@UO]wD@AOUyD@WO]
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G6/12
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,400,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39907
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F399A1779127867
OL,3,CBeatles, boats, and JLR: Mural
OL,4,Ccelebrating town's history nears
OL,5,Ccompletion
OL,7,FThe mural also shows Paralympian
OL,8,Fjudoka Daniel Powell, who won the gold
OL,9,Fmedal in the Men's 73 kg at the 2022
OL,10,FCommonwealth Games.
OL,12,F"I particularly enjoyed painting him,"
OL,13,FStuart said.
OL,15,FA local window cleaner Dennis Mairs
OL,16,Fsaid: "It's superb," pointing at the
OL,17,Fjudoka Daniel Powell and adding: "His
OL,18,Fdad used to train my lads.
OL,20,F"I knew Powell when he was young. I've
OL,21,Fseen them all grow up," he said.
OL,26,@tD@AOUtD@fO]xD@GOUxD@TO]yD@bOU|D@AOU}D@
OL,26,AWO]
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G7/12
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
