FL,400,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39908
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F399A1779127867
OL,3,CBeatles, boats, and JLR: Mural
OL,4,Ccelebrating town's history nears
OL,5,Ccompletion
OL,7,FThe mural took Stuart Harrison about a
OL,8,Fyear to design and stencil.
OL,10,FHe then mapped the steps needed to
OL,11,Fcreate the mural across thousands of
OL,12,Fsheets of paper, each showing
OL,13,Fincremental changes like adding grass,
OL,14,Fa car wing mirror or highlights to add
OL,15,Fa metallic finish.
OL,17,FThen came the task of painting and
OL,18,Fspraying the contours of the piece
OL,19,Fonto the wall. "It was against the
OL,20,Fclock," Stuart said, "Thank God the
OL,21,Fwind didn't blow."
OL,26,@{D@POU|D@GO]|D@VOU}D@RO]
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G8/12
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,400,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39909
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F399A1779127867
OL,3,CBeatles, boats, and JLR: Mural
OL,4,Ccelebrating town's history nears
OL,5,Ccompletion
OL,7,FThe mural is nearing completion, and
OL,8,FStuart only has finishing touches to
OL,9,Fmake - such as adding the registration
OL,10,Fof the very first Ford Anglia to come
OL,11,Foff the Ford Halewood production line
OL,12,Fin 1963, which he was told by a
OL,13,Fresident.
OL,15,F"I could spend the next three weeks
OL,16,Ffiddling until it was perfect, but
OL,17,FI've got to go," he said.
OL,26,@wD@AOUyD@PO]
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G9/12
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,400,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39910
SC,0010
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F399A1779127867
OL,3,CBeatles, boats, and JLR: Mural
OL,4,Ccelebrating town's history nears
OL,5,Ccompletion
OL,7,FKnowsley Council has commissioned
OL,8,Fseveral murals, including in Prescot
OL,9,Fand Huyton, over the past few years in
OL,10,Fa bid to tell the history of the
OL,11,Fborough through bright visuals,
OL,12,Fusually working with artists from
OL,13,FMerseyside.
OL,15,FCouncillor Shelley Powell, Knowsley's
OL,16,Fcabinet member for communities and
OL,17,Fneighbourhoods, said: "The new
OL,18,FHalewood mural is a real celebration
OL,19,Fof stories and memories from the local
OL,20,Fcommunity.
OL,26,@yD@WOU
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}     G10/12
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,400,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39911
SC,0011
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F399A1779127867
OL,3,CBeatles, boats, and JLR: Mural
OL,4,Ccelebrating town's history nears
OL,5,Ccompletion
OL,7,F"It's the latest in a series of murals
OL,8,Facross Knowsley that reflect the
OL,9,Fidentity of different areas. They
OL,10,Fcreate focal points that people can
OL,11,Ftake pride in and transform everyday
OL,12,Fspaces.
OL,14,F"By reflecting local messages and
OL,15,Fshared heritage, these artworks help
OL,16,Fbring communities together and create
OL,17,Fa stronger sense of belonging."
OL,26,@oD@AOUvD@AOUyD@_O]
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}     G11/12
